{"submission_id":"sub_2d6a57853fd0e10b","run_id":"2026-06-20T12-48-52-123Z_1885472-55fd5b19_ingest_meeting-doc-124251","submitted_at":"2026-06-20T13:34:43.902Z","tool_args_sha256":"sha256:2d6a57853fd0e10b1d4c0d417245c9270a51d333d17848c126cb9554275cfff9","schema_version":2,"tool_args":{"source_id":"meeting_doc_124251","observation_kind":"claim","local_observation_id":"claim_meeting_doc_124251_ct_funding_reduction","label":"CTDOT Reduced Funding Allocations","raw_text":"As a result of lowered funding allocations from the Connecticut Legislature to support rail service, CTDOT requested New Haven Line service adjustments commensurate with the new funding level. Metro-North and CTDOT worked collaboratively on a revised service plan, which does not affect New Haven Line service in New York State.","payload":{"claim_text":"As a result of lowered funding allocations from the Connecticut Legislature to support rail service, CTDOT requested New Haven Line service adjustments commensurate with the new funding level. Metro-North and CTDOT worked collaboratively on a revised service plan, which does not affect New Haven Line service in New York State."},"evidence_refs":[{"source_id":"meeting_doc_124251","evidence_id":"meeting_doc_124251#p002_c0008","source_path":"raw/sources/meeting_doc_124251/blocks.jsonl","page_number":2,"block_id":"p002_c0008","text_sha256":"sha256:aef6c0acfc95e3de43f4d63c02a0635c0e4f48dbf18fa1862c968e83e8809a4e","text_source":"raw_text"}]},"validation":{"state":"accepted","issues":[]}}
{"submission_id":"sub_5dcc8b5028c73a4f","run_id":"2026-06-20T12-48-52-123Z_1885472-55fd5b19_ingest_meeting-doc-124251","submitted_at":"2026-06-20T13:35:04.343Z","tool_args_sha256":"sha256:5dcc8b5028c73a4f82fe7e0a6063b5d2167fb1650ea04fdb5e0fd2348d24c4d5","schema_version":2,"tool_args":{"source_id":"meeting_doc_124251","observation_kind":"claim","local_observation_id":"claim_meeting_doc_124251_infrastructure_schedule_support","label":"Schedule Supports Infrastructure Projects","raw_text":"The October 29 schedule supports major MTA C&D, CTDOT and Maintenance of Way projects that require extensive track outages. On-time performance data and ridership and dwell-time analyses were considered and utilized to ensure minimal effects on customers' daily commutes.","payload":{"claim_text":"The October 29 schedule supports major MTA C&D, CTDOT and Maintenance of Way projects that require extensive track outages. On-time performance data and ridership and dwell-time analyses were considered and utilized to ensure minimal effects on customers' daily commutes."},"evidence_refs":[{"source_id":"meeting_doc_124251","evidence_id":"meeting_doc_124251#p001_c0010","source_path":"raw/sources/meeting_doc_124251/blocks.jsonl","page_number":1,"block_id":"p001_c0010","text_sha256":"sha256:3971a0fcb1f9f8c16efba94bcc4ff7d95546a09343e6285e5de89e491690a016","text_source":"raw_text"}]},"validation":{"state":"accepted","issues":[]}}
